Title: Rosecrans (William S.) Papers
AltTitle.descriptive: Correspondence between Abraham Lincoln and William S. Rosecrans
Description.abstract: William Starke Rosecrans (1819-1898) commanded the Army of the Cumberland during the Tullahoma campaign and at the battles of Stone's river and Chickamauga during the U.S. Civil War. The digital collection consists of correspondence with Abraham Lincoln and related documents.
